7\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34241,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/ali-do-not-rebuke\/","url_meta":{"origin":30357,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Blame: Do not excessively rebuke people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abi al-Sa\u2019ib reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not frequently scold others, for scolding leads to resentment and hatred and too much of it is bad manners.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304\u2019 1\/182 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31704,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/ali-dua-answered-supplication\/","url_meta":{"origin":30357,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Dua: Distance between heaven and earth an answered prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Maslamah ibn Muharib reported: It was said to Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWhat is the distance between heaven and earth?\u201d Ali said, \u201cAn answered prayer.\u201d Source: al-Muja\u0304lasah wa Jawa\u0304hir al-\u2018Ilm 2576 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/15\/ali-calamity-sin-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":30357,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Trials: Calamities due to sin, removed by repentance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA trial is not sent down but due to a sin, and it is not lifted but with repentance.\u201d Source: al-Jawa\u0304b al-Ka\u0304fi\u0304 1\/74 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0644\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33777,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/16\/minimum-valid-marriage\/","url_meta":{"origin":30357,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Minimum legal requirements for valid marriage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no marriage unless with a guardian and two credible witnesses. Any marriage contracted with less than that is invalid. If there is a dispute, the ruler is the guardian for one without a guardian.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-doing-spreading-fahishah\/","url_meta":{"origin":30357,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Sin: Doing and spreading vulgarity equal in sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Hassan ibn Kurayb reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cOne who says something vulgar and one who publicizes it are equal in sin.\" Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 324 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u06